		<div class="post_item">
			<p class="usr_cover"><a name_card="82153856" rel="" href="http://www.xiami.com/u/82153856"  title="cntys">  <img src="http://pic.xiami.net/images/avatar_new/1643/821538561447252040_1.jpg" width="50" height="50" alt="cntys" />  </a></p>
